I'm willing to buy it low enough  

781
01:11:59,200 --> 01:12:06,320
down when progress is relatively simple.
But higher up, you start to get to shape  

782
01:12:06,880 --> 01:12:12,000
the way in which you do the exploration.
And it's interesting, we are starting to  

783
01:12:12,000 --> 01:12:17,120
