"Oh, we're not going to go down that path." 

788
01:12:43,120 --> 01:12:47,440
So that starts to look like a set of 
institutions where we are actually  

789
01:12:47,440 --> 01:12:54,640
influencing how we explore the tech tree.
On where you would see these gains from trade,  

790
