01:15:39,840 --> 01:15:43,200
quantity. It's a very deep idea. There's 
another—which you've written a lot about,  

824
01:15:43,200 --> 01:15:52,160
written a textbook about in fact—about ways to 
understand what kinds of things you can compute,  

