835
01:16:46,640 --> 01:16:51,600
Then you understand later, this also contains 
within it the ideas of public-key cryptography. 

836
01:16:51,600 --> 01:16:54,560
Then you understand later, 
that also contains within it  

837
01:16:55,120 --> 01:17:00,800
the ideas people refer to as cryptocurrency.
There's a very deep set of ideas there about  

