1165
01:49:41,600 --> 01:49:45,760
work is and how I get better at it.
In particular, how can I make sure  

1166
01:49:45,760 --> 01:49:49,680
there's some compounding between the 
different people I talk to on the podcast? 

1167
01:49:50,480 --> 01:49:58,480
I worry that instead of this compounding, I build 
up some understanding that's somewhat superficial  

1168
01:49:58,480 --> 01:50:03,440
about a topic, and then it depreciates.
