Maybe it means starting a parallel project in  

1177
01:50:52,880 --> 01:50:55,840
which you do something that is 
actually quite a bit different. 

1178
01:50:55,840 --> 01:51:02,160
There is something really interesting 
about how being very demanding can  

1179
01:51:02,160 --> 01:51:07,360
