1183
01:51:23,840 --> 01:51:27,520
If a million dollars had been at stake, 
would you have put the same effort in? 

1184
01:51:27,520 --> 01:51:35,520
And the answer is no, invariably.
They've tried, but they haven't really tried. 

1185
01:51:36,240 --> 01:51:38,800
I think that's a very familiar 
feeling for all of us. 

1186
01:51:38,800 --> 01:51:50,320
You could do a lot more if you had just the right 
demanding taskmaster standing by you and saying,  

1187
01:51:50,320 --> 01:51:55,600
"Look, you're barely operating here."
I do wonder a little bit about  

1188
01:51:56,800 --> 01:52:01,600
what's the demanding taskmaster?
What can they ask you that is going  

1189
01:52:01,600 --> 01:52:09,600
