1224
01:55:22,480 --> 01:55:26,560
But for you personally, what changed?
There are some things I learned. 

1225
01:55:27,680 --> 01:55:31,120
If I had allocated more time, 
especially after the interview, to  

1226
01:55:32,480 --> 01:55:35,760
