Maybe I should just hire different  

1234
01:56:08,720 --> 01:56:11,840
ones for different topics.
Maybe. There's something about,  

1235
01:56:12,400 --> 01:56:18,720
what problem are you solving for each episode?
As far as I can tell, that's the only way I  

1236
01:56:18,720 --> 01:56:24,560
really understand anything. I get interested in 
something. At first, I don't even have a problem,  

1237
01:56:24,560 --> 01:56:27,680
but there's just some sense that there's some 
contribution to make here, and gradually you  

1238
01:56:27,680 --> 01:56:32,560
hone in, and there's a problem.
Funnily enough, spending time  

1239
01:56:32,560 --> 01:56:39,600
