15 years later, I'll still remember.
Can you describe outside of physics how  

1246
01:57:23,120 --> 01:57:31,280
you learn, of the ones that took three months?
By far the most common thing is there's always  

1247
01:57:31,280 --> 01:57:37,600
some creative artifact. Sometimes it's a 
class. Sometimes it's engagement with a  

1248
01:57:37,600 --> 01:57:45,200
