1259
01:58:39,760 --> 01:58:46,960
How do you make it as jugular as possible?
The higher you can raise the stakes, the better. 

1260
01:58:46,960 --> 01:58:49,120
The interview is in some 
sense high stakes, but also  

1261
01:58:49,120 --> 01:58:54,080
it doesn't necessarily test deep understanding.
I don't think the interview is that high stakes. 

1262
01:58:54,080 --> 01:58:57,760
You're not writing a book about special 
relativity, and you're not trying to write a  

1263
01:58:57,760 --> 01:59:05,520
book that replaces whatever the existing standard 
textbook is. That's a really high stake. By the  

1264
01:59:05,520 --> 01:59:16,240
