1275
02:00:04,960 --> 02:00:07,680
It’s entertaining but not 
necessarily anything else. 

1276
02:00:07,680 --> 02:00:12,240
It’s such an easy way to get out of the thing.
In fact, it makes it easier because instead  

1277
02:00:12,240 --> 02:00:17,280
